data.description: Be one with the forest! Surrounded by old growth trees in the heart of the quaint logging town of Gilchrist, this warm and inviting home offers plenty of room to live, love and relax. The spacious single level home features knotty pine paneling in several rooms, original (genuine) hardwood floors, a wood burning fireplace for cold winter nights, formal living room and dining room and large family room. The kitchen has all brand new stainless steel appliances and charming natural wood cabinets. Make happy memories on the covered patio and in the large, fenced yard that is perfect for outdoor games, barbecues and bird watching. The large 2-car attached garage offers plenty of storage with shelving and an additional storage room.
